name: UIDocument.ChangeKind
desc: Constants for specifying the kind of change to a document.

items.name: case done
items.desc: A change has been made to the document.

items.name: case undone
items.desc: A change to the document has been undone.

items.name: case redone
items.desc: An undone change to the document has been redone.

items.name: case cleared
items.desc: The document is cleared of outstanding changes.
